==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Heptagonal
<hw>Hep*tag"o*nal</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>heptagonal</ets>.]</ety> <def>Having seven angles or
sides.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Heptagonal numbers</b></col> <fld>(Arith.)</fld>, <cd>the
numbers of the series 1, 7, 18, 34, 55, etc., being figurate numbers
formed by adding successively the terms of the arithmetical series 1, 6,
11, 16, 21, etc.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Heptagynia</ent>⟦br⟧
\'d8
